    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Strategy of Upgrades, the Thrill of Defense<br>Your choices—and your luck—will decide the battle.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[ Game Overview ]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Checkmate Defense” is a strategic auto-battle tower defense game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summon and merge turrets from 1★ to 6★ to stop relentless enemy waves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During combat, every decision—merging, selling, positioning, and upgrading—becomes a decisive move that reshapes the battlefield.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player Movement</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move using WASD or the Arrow Keys (↑ ← ↓ →).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/5fab84eaf8440492c3b114478dcf6d47.poster.avif?t=1768920431\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/5fab84eaf8440492c3b114478dcf6d47.webm?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/5fab84eaf8440492c3b114478dcf6d47.mp4?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Turret Summoning</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press Q to summon a turret.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※ Higher-rarity turrets have increased summon chances based on the player’s Luck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/dba946b29aff7eba36f1590fe48c52ae.poster.avif?t=1768920431\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/dba946b29aff7eba36f1590fe48c52ae.webm?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/dba946b29aff7eba36f1590fe48c52ae.mp4?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Turret Merging</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press E to merge turrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※ 1★–5★ Turrets: Merge two identical turrets to obtain a random turret of the next tier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※ 6★ Turrets: Spend 200 coins and select two 5★ turrets from the recipe to summon a 6★ turret.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/205e4a1fd37fdf6157da19dbe267af42.poster.avif?t=1768920431\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/205e4a1fd37fdf6157da19dbe267af42.webm?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/205e4a1fd37fdf6157da19dbe267af42.mp4?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Turret Selling</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press R to sell a turret.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※ 6★ turrets cannot be sold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/eb238e747a401fd0eca789efd36e43fa.poster.avif?t=1768920431\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/eb238e747a401fd0eca789efd36e43fa.webm?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/eb238e747a401fd0eca789efd36e43fa.mp4?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Turret Placement</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press Z to pick up a turret, and X to place it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/8c1e23b129d7a9ceeeac9b361b7e8733.poster.avif?t=1768920431\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/8c1e23b129d7a9ceeeac9b361b7e8733.webm?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/8c1e23b129d7a9ceeeac9b361b7e8733.mp4?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mines</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approach a mine and press the number keys (1–5) to assign a turret to it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/6c582c6fac82003f929338b8cf3f08a4.poster.avif?t=1768920431\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/6c582c6fac82003f929338b8cf3f08a4.webm?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/6c582c6fac82003f929338b8cf3f08a4.mp4?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In-Game Upgrades</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain higher-rarity upgrades based on the player’s Luck during a run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/33ab73d03526c2a902b3b68468afaa55.poster.avif?t=1768920431\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/33ab73d03526c2a902b3b68468afaa55.webm?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/33ab73d03526c2a902b3b68468afaa55.mp4?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lobby Upgrades</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn resources by clearing Boss Waves and unlock various upgrades in the Lobby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/7b616eaff6693eafcc2298131c634eb3.poster.avif?t=1768920431\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/7b616eaff6693eafcc2298131c634eb3.webm?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/7b616eaff6693eafcc2298131c634eb3.mp4?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collection</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turrets discovered through summoning and merging are unlocked in the Collection, where you can view their details.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/dc6e41129e360308b29cebe67527594c.poster.avif?t=1768920431\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/dc6e41129e360308b29cebe67527594c.webm?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4313540/extras/dc6e41129e360308b29cebe67527594c.mp4?t=1768920431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On a battlefield of chaos where Solterian, Nethral, Elynsha, and Fenrok—four races—fight together,<br>the player stands as the King, commanding the final line of defense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, prove your choices and your luck in Checkmate Defense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
